snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedValidation

client = AsyncSeedValidation(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.create(
        decimal=2.2,
        even=100,
        name="foo",
        shape="SQUARE",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
